# Additional Questions Answered

Node selector

apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: nginx-zone-f
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: nginx-zone-f
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: nginx-zone-f
    spec:
      nodeSelector:
        topology.kubernetes.io/zone: us-east-1f
      containers:
      - name: nginx
        image: 35.153.133.45:5000/nginx
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80


